author: The Current
description:
Confused about the song title "Bovine Excision"? Samia explains
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube 

Singer-songwriter Samia releases her second full-length album, 'Bloodless,' on April 25, 2025. One of the tracks on the album is "Bovine Excision"; Samia explains the origins of this song title in an interview with The Current's Jessica Paxton.

Samia’s 2025 album, 'Bloodless,' is available on @grandjurymusic.
